descriptionShort: Singular is the World’s most intelligent investment management app
title: Singular

creator: Singular Capital
descriptionHtml:
Welcome to Singular. Choose from our comprehensive set of alpha-oriented cryptocurrency portfolios managed by industry veterans, hedge funds and blockchain technical advisories.

Singular aims to democratize cryptocurrency investing by harnessing artificial intelligence, machine learning, and quantitative analysis to make cryptocurrency investing accessible to everyone.

Get access to Singular’s Multi-Strategy Funds, and put your crypto in motion. Invest in Bitcoin (BTC), Ethereum (ETH), Stellar (XLM), Solana (SOL), Aave (AAVE), Compound (COMP), Enjin (ENJ), Ripple, (XRP), Polygon (MATIC), Uniswap (UNI), Convex Finance (CVX), Chainlink (LINK), Basic Attention Token (BAT) and more in an optimized risk and return using Modern portfolio theory, active risk management and quantitative finance. All Singular funds are battle-tested and built for scale.

Start investing in cryptocurrency with our institutional-grade portfolios built by industry experts:

1. Choose a Fund to Invest
2. Deposit Crypto or Manual Bank Deposit
3. Track Your Crypto Portfolio Anywhere
4. Sell Anytime with No-Lockups

FIAT ON-RAMPS

* We Support various fiat deposits
* Wire transfers allowed in or out with low fees

INSTITUTIONAL-GRADE SECURITY

-Singular uses industry-leading security
-Hardware-based online vault with no single point of failure

24/7 Wealth Concierge
-Our Customer support team is available around the clock
-Our team is ready to walk you through every step of your investing experience

Disclaimer:
The content contained herein is for informational purposes only and does not constitute recommendation, investment or legal advice.
Cryptocurrencies are highly volatile and there can be substantial risk of losing money and may not be suitable for every user.

descriptionShort: Singular is the World’s most intelligent investment management app
title: Singular

creator: Singular Capital
descriptionHtml:
The Singular Invest app is packed with a wide range of features that empower users to manage and grow their thematic investments effectively. With a seamless user experience and advanced features, Singular Invest empowers users to take control of their financial future.
Get access to Singular Multi-Strategy Funds, and know how to invest in Crypto and start investing in a portfolio of the top Metaverse assets, DeFI tokens, High Yield products, algorithmically traded Bitcoin, and fractionalized top NFTs. These portfolios are constructed by experts and rebalanced periodically to maximize returns.
Singular utilizes advanced algorithms and artificial intelligence to provide personalized investment recommendations. The Singular app considers factors such as users' financial goals, risk tolerance, and market trends to offer tailored investment suggestions. This feature ensures that users can make informed decisions and optimize their portfolios.
The app offers a diverse range of investment options, including stocks, bonds, mutual funds, and exchange-traded funds (ETFs). Users have the flexibility to choose from various asset classes and investment strategies to diversify their portfolios according to their preferences.
Singular Invest provides real-time market data, news, and insights to keep users up-to-date with the latest financial information. Users can access real-time stock prices, charts, and other relevant market information, enabling them to make informed investment decisions based on current market conditions.
Security is a top priority for Singular App. The app employs robust encryption and authentication measures to safeguard users' personal and financial information. Additionally, the app offers a user-friendly interface that makes navigation and portfolio management seamless and intuitive.
We provide reliable customer support to assist users with any queries or issues they may encounter. Users can reach out to the support team through various channels, such as in-app chat, email, or phone.
We combine advanced thematic technology, personalized recommendations, real-time market data, and educational resources to offer users a comprehensive investment experience. Whether users are experienced investors or just starting their investment journey, Singular Invest equips them with the tools and information needed to make informed investment decisions and grow their wealth effectively.

Disclaimer:
The content contained herein is for informational purposes only and does not constitute a recommendation, investment, or legal advice.
Cryptocurrencies are highly volatile, and there can be a substantial risk of losing money and may not be suitable for every user.
